<br>
I upped my Psychology score, bought a high-Q Aggression Enhancer, and MAN OH MAN does it ever work like a charm!<br>
<br>
I was pulling monsters off the doc first try 9-and-half times out of 10. And when the first try did not work, the second one always did.<br>
<br>
In a way, this has me really stoked, but in a way it's really sad. It means all those tanks out there who have let my doc die over and over when she was yelling for help are either mis-informed or just plain lazy. Either way, they are not doing their jobs, when they easily could be.<br>
<br>
Heh, and I guess in a way it's a sad comment on AO. Something actually works the way it's supposed to, and I get all excited and happy about it. Bleh.<br>
